To scan channels use:
	$ scan ${PREFIX}/share/linuxtv-dvb/dvb-[tsc]/[satellite] > \
		~/.szap/channels.conf

To sintonize it:
	$ szap -r "Channel Name"

To view it:
	$ mplayer /dev/dvb/adapter0/dvr0

===========================================================================
